NB: **This version is forked from SimpleRL and needs to be refactored to OO for this project**
Please remove this notice when it has been done!

https://github.com/nrkn/SimpleRL

This only works with GNU Smalltalk.

Why?  Most Smalltalks use an image-based development system, so they
tend to function only within their own sandbox.  GNU Smalltalk
provides some custom syntax to enable traditional file-based
development.
